 &HT;    AMERICAN TROOPS IN BOSNIA
 &HT;    With BOSNIA-TROOPS-BOX-$ADV03.
 &HT;    For Use Saturday, Oct. 3 And Thereafter.
 &HT;    By SUSANNAH A. NESMITH 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Fort Hood soldiers stationed at the six U.S. installations in
Bosnia:
</P>
