little metal, but the object that went on display in Wright State
University's Student Union started a revolution. It's the 1902
Wright Glider, or rather a faithful reproduction of the glider that
proved the Wright brothers' design for a flying machine. (Gaffney,
Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
