<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-30 13:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2042 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOOD-SWORDFISH-2TAKES     09-30 0892
