PASSPORT-AIDS (Los Angeles) _ The West Coast's biggest AIDS
fund-raiser _ Passport _ is a dinner, fashion show, circus and rock
concert starring Elizabeth Taylor, Magic Johnson and k.d. lang,
with numerous stars modeling the fashions of leading designers down
the runway. By Barbara De Witt. 
. 
