<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-30 17:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2605 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-MORTGAGE-RATES-NYT     09-30 0724
