<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-30 20:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2906 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-CONGRESS-675&AMP;     09-30 1237
