named a modest-spoken Iowan, Kerry Killinger, as its CEO. Today
Killinger is by all accounts still the unassuming Midwesterner, but
Washington Mutual is hardly the lackluster thrift that barely
operated outside King County, Wash.
</P>
<P>
   By Bill Virgin. (Story will move in the ``f'' category.)
