<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-CLINTON-SCHIPPERS-NYT, which
moved in ``w'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I don't want to write books or go on television or be a big
star. My philosophy is come out here, do the job and get out, go
home.''
</P>
<P>
   _DAVID P. SCHIPPERS, chief investigator for the House Judiciary
Committee.
</P>
