   (NYT5) UNDATED -- Sept. 30, 1998 -- CIR-JIGSAW-GAME, 9-30 --
Daffy and company entertain players who solve the Looney Tunes
Cosmic Capers Animated Jigsaws. As with any toy transported from
the physical world to the computer screen, there is the question of
whether a digital interface adds anything to the experience. In
this case, it does. (New York Times Photo)
