<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-30 22:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3093 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-BURN-PLAYOFFS-TEX     09-30 0709
